# GMAIL

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User "ingo.fruend@googlemail.com"
PassCmd "lpass show --password 3709079601136425669"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail
UseNamespace yes

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.Mail/gmail/INBOX
